com.ibm.team.build.ant.task

Class BuildToolkitVersionTask

  • java.lang.Object
    • Task
      • com.ibm.team.build.ant.task.BuildToolkitVersionTask

  • public class BuildToolkitVersionTask
extends Task
    Stores the version of the build toolkit that this task is running from in a property.

    Required attributes are

    • versionProperty - The property into which version will be stored
